BT 1 0 0 1 30 346.8756 Tm (     1. Purpose) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 338.4756 Tm (     This procedure defines the mandatory steps for performing a product changeover on NEXUS assembly lines. The) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 330.0756 Tm (     changeover procedure ensures complete removal of all components from the previous product before the next product) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 321.6756 Tm (     is introduced, preventing cross-contamination and component mix-up between different NEXUS products.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 313.2756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 304.8756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 296.4756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 288.0756 Tm (     2. Scope) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 279.6756 Tm (     Applicable to all NEXUS assembly lines \(AL-001 through AL-005\) at Riverside when changing from one NEXUS) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 271.2756 Tm (     product to another. This includes changeovers between any NEXUS product variants \(CK MB, B2M, Troponin,) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 262.8756 Tm (     D-Dimer, etc.\).) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 254.4756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 246.0756 Tm (      WARNING: MINIMUM CHANGEOVER TIME: 30 MINUTES. Production of the new product MUST NOT begin) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 237.6756 Tm (      until at least 30 minutes have elapsed since the last unit of the previous product exited the assembly line.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 229.2756 Tm (      This time is required to complete all 8 items on the clearance checklist. Any deviation from this minimum) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 220.8756 Tm (      time must be documented as a non-conformity per SOP-QA-010.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 212.4756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 204.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 195.6756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 187.2756 Tm (     3. References) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 178.8756 Tm (     - FMEA-CKMB-001: FMEA for NEXUS CK MB) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 170.4756 Tm (     - FMEA-B2M-001: FMEA for NEXUS B2M) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 162.0756 Tm (     - SOP-QA-010: Non-Conformity Reporting) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 153.6756 Tm (     - FORM-ASM-003: Assembly Line Clearance Checklist) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 145.2756 Tm (     - INV-2024-0067: Investigation - Assembly Line Mix-up \(reference case\)) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 136.8756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 128.4756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 120.0756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 111.6756 Tm (     4. Procedure) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 103.2756 Tm  T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 94.87559 Tm (     4.1 Pre-Changeover) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 86.47559 Tm (     4.1.1 Confirm that the last production lot of the current product has been completed and all units have exited the) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 78.07559 Tm (     assembly line.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 69.67559 Tm (     4.1.2 Record the completion time on FORM-ASM-003.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 61.27559 Tm (     4.1.3 Start the changeover timer \(electronic timer on line control panel\).) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 52.87559 Tm (     4.1.4 Notify the area supervisor that changeover is beginning.) Tj T* ET
BT 1 0 0 1 30 44.47559 Tm  T* ET
 
